OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope urges 'radical'       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclimate response in        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fexclusive BBC message      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In a message recorded exclusively for  
OL,6, the BBC, Pope Francis has called on    
OL,7, world leaders meeting next week at the 
OL,8, UN Climate conference in Glasgow to    
OL,9, provide "effective responses" to the   
OL,10, environment emergency and offer        
OL,11, "concrete hope" to future generations. 
OL,13,FSpeaking from the Vatican for BBC Radio
OL,14,F4's Thought for the Day, the Pope      
OL,15,Ftalked of crises including the Covid-19
OL,16,Fpandemic, climate change and economic  
OL,17,Fdifficulties, and urged the world to   
OL,18,Frespond to them with vision and radical
OL,19,Fdecisions, so as not to "waste         
OL,20,Fopportunities" that the current        
OL,21,Fchallenges present.                    
